{"tid":2498913,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"呢期除咗MIRROR之外，原來有個叫阿俊嘅都接好多廣告","createTime":"2021-04-21T13:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T13:44:19.000Z","uid":219969,"like":92,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"79b9ae9b9d7a60d91d27a600d9a30bef28854e23","tid":2498913,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:15:17.000Z","msg":"佢叫做黃俊豪，以前係model，同何超蓮拍過拖。2020年6月左右加盟邵氏、TVB，近期喺愛回家做過路人角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV5zcSitRKzcQiLW6deiazgDLwxMUK2g9BVcc4i7MVAhJ?filename=qJECorS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJECorS.png&h=1aebe6fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXGcmbmC9dpgDRL8Y9WdLDymnmmbPXEU9jDZfLEgj2uFM?filename=i0SXori.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi0SXori.jpg&h=c8c9923d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote><span class=\"small\">我哋最近留意到廣告商特別鍾意用黃俊豪(TVB基本藝人、邵氏藝人)賣廣告，包括維他、滴露、KFC、周生生等，廣告之多甚至比得上TVB一線明星，實在令人震驚。</span></blockquote><br />\n你哋係咪唔識佢呢？樓主都唔識佢，但TVB戰線ADMIN話佢好多廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcZ1YNMCLbzT79NVkxz7LvtyKgB1vDTM1Dbc9oJR7DeJX?filename=ax2gDZT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fax2gDZT.jpg&h=8427cf40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n斷咗成年廣告嘅KFC都特登搵佢拍廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmS5BZ7N1B2RBZzzZ4gDVUz4yBag4Fr6U8z2MX1YWjUauZ?filename=zibxcku.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzibxcku.png&h=19c37b71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然滴露搵咗林嘉欣代言，但係都要搭多個TVB偽人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXpjnYaYdAiSYcCGVePJEvBsSmAFxWEBgKPMxHh851cGi?filename=FGx4NUi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFGx4NUi.png&h=9c41d05c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n維他..維他水都要廣告？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdnXoAFCibXWLs6FDYaJFi3ZYxDe71ohhQEvqaZmA9piR?filename=cWyoi0P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcWyoi0P.jpg&h=fdd1ea36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食屎啦滴露同維他，都唔知咩廣告策略黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">維他派嬲嬲，滴露派慘慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">🚫 維他飲品 🚫</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vitavitasoy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvitavitasoy&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=714c5fdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/vitavitasoy</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://pili.app/pg/n1B411hn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpili.app%2Fpg%2Fn1B411hn&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=c746a11f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pili.app/pg/n1B411hn</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPtd5HntdYKxYMiMB7Ghp24eAEnjYBB2wCetucpUUEo56?filename=Crco3tO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCrco3tO.png&h=8d850086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">🚫 滴露 🚫</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dettolhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdettolhk&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=075f04bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dettolhk</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://pili.app/pg/2q9fomY03\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/lin